#. [modify_side]
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios/05_A_Subterranean_Struggle.cfg:146
#: data/campaigns/Under_the_Burning_Suns/scenarios/05_A_Subterranean_Struggle.cfg:195
